title: EYL #200 How to Become a 9 to 5 Millionaire
itunes:title: EYL #200 How to Become a 9 to 5 Millionaire
description:
In episode 200 we spoke to Jemal King aka 9 to 5 Millionaire about his amazing journey to become a multi millionaire real estate investor and enthrepenur all while working as a full time police officer. 

This episode is a must watch for anyone that has goals of achieving wealth and is still working a 9 to 5 job. #realestate #Chicago #earnyourleisure
